WHAT IS IT?
-----------

  'In_And_Out' is a Workbench game played on a 10 by 10 tiles
board. The goal is to go from the top of the board to the Exit (a
tile marked with an 'E'), which is located on the bottom. Try to
get to the Exit in the least number of moves.

  To complicate the game a little bit, on some levels, there are
'Mystery' tiles (tiles marked by a '?' sign) which change your
destination every time you get on them. Also, some tiles may be
replaced by 'Holes', where you cannot move to thereafter...

  At the end of each level, the game shows some statistics like:
how many moves you did on the current level, the level where you
did the least amount of moves and the average amount of moves made
on each level.

  Try to complete all 50 levels of the game...

  Have fun!

